{"tid":180301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[出街帶遮呀]雷雨帶正靠近 未來兩三小時影響本港3月31日","createTime":"2017-03-31T00:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T02:19:01.000Z","uid":54733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"572005ebb2f3f62448fd91e3d43dffc6bdf135b3","tid":180301,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:31:15.000Z","msg":"【08:15更新】現時氣溫22℃，相對濕度百分之95。與冷鋒相關的雷雨帶正從廣東內陸靠近，並會在未來兩三小時影響本港。市民應提高警惕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潮濕的偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港今早有霧，港內的能見度降至1,000米以下。此外 ，位於廣東北部的一道冷鋒正為該區帶來雷雨，預料該冷鋒會在今日日間橫過沿岸地區 。<br />\n<br />\n本港今日大致多雲，有幾陣雨，初時有霧。吹和緩東至東南風。日間轉吹清勁北風，雨 勢漸轉頻密及有狂風雷暴。氣溫由最高約23℃顯著下降至今晚約16℃。<br />\n<br />\n展望：未來兩三日天晴乾燥，早上天氣清涼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56503190&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56503190%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170331&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=14336804\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56503190%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170331&h=6c5e87b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56503190&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170331</a>"},{"pid":"a4cd61c04a84add2223347440e1ac18c8797b200","tid":180301,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:46:34.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c1732c1f2c864ca041f3fcaaa774039bc3ec69cc","tid":180301,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以落大d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":